{"thag6.1:0.1":"Theragatha 6.1 ","thag6.1:0.2":"Chakkanipata ","thag6.1:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag6.1:0.4":"Uruvelakassapattheragatha ","thag6.1:1.1":"“Disvana patihirani, ","thag6.1:1.2":"gotamassa yasassino; ","thag6.1:1.3":"Na tavaham panipatim, ","thag6.1:1.4":"issamanena vancito. ","thag6.1:2.1":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","thag6.1:2.2":"codesi narasarathi; ","thag6.1:2.3":"Tato me asi samvego, ","thag6.1:2.4":"abbhuto lomahamsano. ","thag6.1:3.1":"Pubbe jatilabhutassa, ","thag6.1:3.2":"ya me siddhi parittika; ","thag6.1:3.3":"Taham tada nirakatva, ","thag6.1:3.4":"pabbajim jinasasane. ","thag6.1:4.1":"Pubbe yannena santuttho, ","thag6.1:4.2":"kamadhatupurakkhato; ","thag6.1:4.3":"Paccha raganca dosanca, ","thag6.1:4.4":"mohancapi samuhanim. ","thag6.1:5.1":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","thag6.1:5.2":"dibbacakkhu visodhitam; ","thag6.1:5.3":"Iddhima paracittannu, ","thag6.1:5.4":"dibbasotanca papunim. ","thag6.1:6.1":"Yassa catthaya pabbajito, ","thag6.1:6.2":"agarasmanagariyam; ","thag6.1:6.3":"So me attho anuppatto, ","thag6.1:6.4":"sabbasamyojanakkhayo”ti. ","thag6.1:6.5":"… Uruvelakassapo thero …. "}